divs: Sighting Detailshalfway up the dirt road getting into mataguay scout reservation in san diego county, off to the north a few hundred yards was a pulsating red light, it wasn't a fire, and i know it was not an airplane, it was to dark to see exactly what, but with the few glimmers left of sunlight i could tell what it wasn't. There were sheriffs police and fire trucks but no paramedics, they were sure to to let anybody near the area, there was no smoke or fire, just the red pulsing light, about an hour later when we wee heading back down the dirt road there was nothing there, no lights no cops, no nothing.
